            />
          </picture>
          
          <figcaption class="p9 d-flex flex-column d-flex_r flex-justify-between">
            <span>Interface Design</span>
            <span>8 June, 2020</span>
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
        
        <h3 class="h3 mb-1">Mentorship Match — How a simple LinkedIn feature can boost diversity</h3>
        
        <p class="p5">
          LinkedIn is on a clear mission to make professionals more successful by connecting the global workforce and as we learned — diversity and success go hand in hand
